OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,FThe Bishop of Liverpool Right Reverend
OL,7,FDr John Perumbalath has stepped down
OL,8,Ffrom his role following allegations of
OL,9,Fsexual assault and harassment.
OL,11,FIn a letter sent to clergy in his
OL,12,Fdiocese on Thursday he said he is
OL,13,F"retiring" from his role because he
OL,14,Fdoes not wish to be a "distraction"
OL,15,Ffor "this incredible diocese and its
OL,16,Fpeople whom it has been an honour and
OL,17,Fjoy to serve".
