OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,FThe move comes just days after a
OL,7,FChannel 4 News reported that the
OL,8,Fsenior bishop has been accused of
OL,9,Fsexual misconduct by two women,
OL,10,Fincluding another bishop, which he has
OL,11,Fdenied.
OL,13,FOne woman accused Dr Perumbalath of
OL,14,Fkissing her without consent and
OL,15,Fgroping her, and a female bishop
OL,16,Faccused him of sexual harassment. Both
OL,17,Fincidents allegedly took place in
OL,18,FEssex in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
