OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,FIn his letter, the Bishop said: "Since
OL,7,Fthose allegations were made I have
OL,8,Fconsistently maintained that I have
OL,9,Fnot done anything wrong and continue
OL,10,Fto do so.
OL,12,F"Since the claims were made in 2023
OL,13,Fthey have been investigated and
OL,14,Fconsidered by experts from the
OL,15,FNational Safeguarding Team and had
OL,16,Ffound them unsubstantiated.
OL,18,F"The first allegation was also
OL,19,Finvestigated by the police resulting
OL,20,Fin no further action."
