OL,6,FHe added his decision was "not a
OL,7,Fresignation occasioned by fault or by
OL,8,Fany admission of liability".
OL,10,FHis statement went on: "I do not wish
OL,11,Fthis story to become a distraction for
OL,12,Fthis incredible diocese and its people
OL,13,Fwhom it has been an honour and joy to
OL,14,Fserve.
