OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,F"This is not a resignation occasioned
OL,7,Fby fault or by any admission of
OL,8,Fliability. Rather it has become clear
OL,9,Fthat stepping back from my ministry
OL,10,Fand waiting for the completion of
OL,11,Ffurther reviews would mean a long
OL,12,Fperiod of uncertainty for the diocese
OL,13,Fand all those who serve it.
OL,15,F"I have taken this decision for my own
OL,16,Fwell-being, my family and the best
OL,17,Finterests of the diocese. The exact
OL,18,Fdate when my role will formally end is
OL,19,Fnot yet determined. There are
OL,20,Fprotocols to observe that I will now
OL,21,Fbe attending to.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
