OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,FBishop Perumbalath said he has
OL,7,Fcomplied with any investigation from
OL,8,Fthe National Safeguarding Team (NST).
OL,10,FPolice concluded no further action was
OL,11,Fneeded, while the Church of England
OL,12,Fconcluded there was no case to answer
OL,13,Fin a matter of alleged misconduct
OL,14,Fwhile a legal timeframe to investigate
OL,15,Fa second complaint had expired.
OL,17,FFollowing the allegations, six senior
OL,18,Fclergy said the former Bishop's
OL,19,Fposition was "untenable" and called
OL,20,Ffor him to step down from his role.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
