OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,F"Having listened to clergy,
OL,7,Fcongregations and staff at the
OL,8,Fdiocesan offices and the cathedral, it
OL,9,Fis with deep regret that the senior
OL,10,Fleadership of the diocese of Liverpool
OL,11,Ffeel that the position of the Rt Revd
OL,12,FDr John Perumbalath is currently
OL,13,Funtenable," they said.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
