OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,F"We believe that the allegations made
OL,7,Fby the female bishop need to be fully
OL,8,Fand properly investigated. We also
OL,9,Fbelieve that while these proper
OL,10,Finvestigations are conducted the
OL,11,Fbishop of Liverpool will need to step
OL,12,Faside from all ministry in the diocese
OL,13,Fof Liverpool."
OL,15,FRight Reverend Dr John Perumbalath's
OL,16,Fresignation will now put pressure on
OL,17,Fthe Archbishop of York who is reported
OL,18,Fto have been aware of the allegations
OL,19,Fwhen the Rt Rev Dr Perumbalath was
OL,20,Fenthroned in April 2023.
