OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool steps down amid
OL,4,Csexual assault allegations
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Archbishop of York
OL,7,FStephen Cottrell said: "I acknowledge
OL,8,Fthe decision made by the Rt Revd Dr
OL,9,FJohn Perumbalath to resign from active
OL,10,Fministry in the Church of England. I
OL,11,Frespect his decision and thank him for
OL,12,Fhis ministry.
OL,14,F"My thoughts and prayers continue to
OL,15,Fbe with all those who have been
OL,16,Faffected by this situation.
OL,26,@oD@XOUvD@AOU
